INFN-LScan version 0.1
======================

This is a decent lightweight md5 directory based file checksum tool
It also scans dirs for known rootkits and malicious files

It is easy to use, check out the help by running lscan -h after you move it to /usr/sbin/ and chmod +x


INSTALLATION

To install this module type the following:

   perl Makefile.PL
   make
   make test
   make install
   cp lib/lscan.pl /usr/bin/lscan
   chmod +x /usr/bin/lscan



DEPENDENCIES

This module requires these other modules and libraries:

DBI
File::Find
Digest::MD5
Getopt::Long;


